ex2treLoopRecipients.name: ex2treLoopRecipients
ex2treLoopRecipients.description: Loop Recipients is the number of recipients that failed recipient resolution because of recipient loops.

ex2treMessagesChipped.name: ex2treMessagesChipped
ex2treMessagesChipped.description: Messages Chipped is the total number of copies of the same message that were created during recipient resolution to control the number of envelope recipients in a single message.

ex2treMessagesCreated.name: ex2treMessagesCreated
ex2treMessagesCreated.description: Messages Created is the number of messages that were created during recipient resolution.

ex2treMessagesRetried.name: ex2treMessagesRetried
ex2treMessagesRetried.description: Messages Retried is the number of messages that were scheduled for retry during recipient resolution.

ex2treUnresolvedOrgRecipients.name: ex2treUnresolvedOrgRecipients
ex2treUnresolvedOrgRecipients.description: Unresolved Org Recipients is the number of unresolved recipients from an authoritative domain that were detected during recipient resolution.

ex2treUnresolvedOrgSenders.name: ex2treUnresolvedOrgSenders
ex2treUnresolvedOrgSenders.description: Unresolved Org Senders is the number of unresolved senders from an authoritative domain that were detected during recipient resolution.

ex2TransportRoutingTable.name: ex2TransportRoutingTable
ex2TransportRoutingTable.description: A table containing performance information for instances of 'MSExchangeTransport Routing' objects.

ex2TransportRoutingEntry.name: ex2TransportRoutingEntry
ex2TransportRoutingEntry.description: Performance information for one particular instance of 'MSExchangeTransport Routing' object.

ex2troRoutingNDRsTotal.name: ex2troRoutingNDRsTotal
ex2troRoutingNDRsTotal.description: Routing NDRs Total is the number of recipients NDRed by routing.

ex2troRoutingTableCalculateTotal.name: ex2troRoutingTableCalculateTotal
ex2troRoutingTableCalculateTotal.description: Routing Tables Calculated Total is the number of times that routing tables have been calculated.

ex2troRoutingTablesChangedTotal.name: ex2troRoutingTablesChangedTotal
ex2troRoutingTablesChangedTotal.description: Routing Tables Changed Total is the number of times routing tables have changed.

ex2TransportSmtpReceiveTable.name: ex2TransportSmtpReceiveTable
ex2TransportSmtpReceiveTable.description: A table containing performance information for instances of 'MSExchangeTransport SmtpReceive' objects.

ex2TransportSmtpReceiveEntry.name: ex2TransportSmtpReceiveEntry
ex2TransportSmtpReceiveEntry.description: Performance information for one particular instance of 'MSExchangeTransport SmtpReceive' object.

ex2tsrAverageBytesPerConnection.name: ex2tsrAverageBytesPerConnection
ex2tsrAverageBytesPerConnection.description: Average Bytes/Connection is the average number of bytes received per connection.

ex2tsrAverageBytesPerMessage.name: ex2tsrAverageBytesPerMessage
ex2tsrAverageBytesPerMessage.description: Average Bytes/Message is the average number of message bytes per inbound message received.

ex2tsrAverageMessagePerConnectin.name: ex2tsrAverageMessagePerConnectin
ex2tsrAverageMessagePerConnectin.description: Average Messages/Connection is the average number of messages received per connection.

ex2tsrAverageRecipientPerMessage.name: ex2tsrAverageRecipientPerMessage
ex2tsrAverageRecipientPerMessage.description: Average Recipients/Message is the average number of recipients per inbound message received.

ex2tsrBytesReceivedTotal.name: ex2tsrBytesReceivedTotal
ex2tsrBytesReceivedTotal.description: Bytes Received Total is the total number of bytes received.

ex2tsrBytesReceivedPerSec.name: ex2tsrBytesReceivedPerSec
ex2tsrBytesReceivedPerSec.description: Bytes Received/sec is the number of bytes received per second.

ex2tsrConnectionsCreatedPerSec.name: ex2tsrConnectionsCreatedPerSec
ex2tsrConnectionsCreatedPerSec.description: Connections Created/sec is the number of new connections to the SMTP server that are established each second.

ex2tsrConnectionsCurrent.name: ex2tsrConnectionsCurrent
ex2tsrConnectionsCurrent.description: Connections Current is the number of inbound connections to the SMTP server.

ex2tsrConnectionsTotal.name: ex2tsrConnectionsTotal
ex2tsrConnectionsTotal.description: Connections Total is the total number of connections ever made to the SMTP server.

ex2tsrDisconnectionsByAgents.name: ex2tsrDisconnectionsByAgents
ex2tsrDisconnectionsByAgents.description: Disconnections By Agents is the number of inbound connections that are dropped by Agent actions.

ex2tsrDisconnectByAgentPerSecond.name: ex2tsrDisconnectByAgentPerSecond
ex2tsrDisconnectByAgentPerSecond.description: Disconnections by Agents/second is the number of inbound connections that are dropped by Agent actions per second.

ex2tsrMessageBytesReceivedTotal.name: ex2tsrMessageBytesReceivedTotal
ex2tsrMessageBytesReceivedTotal.description: Message Bytes Received Total is the total number of bytes in messages received and committed to database. This includes the headers that are inserted by the SMTP server and is the actual number of bytes that are written to database.

ex2tsrMessageBytesReceivedPerSec.name: ex2tsrMessageBytesReceivedPerSec
ex2tsrMessageBytesReceivedPerSec.description: Message Bytes Received/sec is the number of bytes received in messages each second.

ex2tsrMessagesReceivedTotal.name: ex2tsrMessagesReceivedTotal
ex2tsrMessagesReceivedTotal.description: Messages Received Total is the number of messages received by the SMTP server.

ex2tsrMessagesReceivedPerSec.name: ex2tsrMessagesReceivedPerSec
ex2tsrMessagesReceivedPerSec.description: Messages Received/sec is the number of messages received by the SMTP server each second.

ex2tsrMessagesRefusedForSize.name: ex2tsrMessagesRefusedForSize
ex2tsrMessagesRefusedForSize.description: Messages Refused for Size is the number of messages that were rejected because they were too big.

ex2tsrRecipientsAcceptedTotal.name: ex2tsrRecipientsAcceptedTotal
ex2tsrRecipientsAcceptedTotal.description: Recipients Accepted Total is the number of recipients accepted.

ex2tsrTarpittingDelaysAnonymous.name: ex2tsrTarpittingDelaysAnonymous
ex2tsrTarpittingDelaysAnonymous.description: Tarpitting Delays Anonymous is the total number of tarpitting delays on anonymous sessions.

ex2tsrTarpittngDelayAuthenticate.name: ex2tsrTarpittngDelayAuthenticate
ex2tsrTarpittngDelayAuthenticate.description: Tarpitting Delays Authenticated is the total number of tarpitting delays on authenticated sessions.

ex2TransportSmtpSendTable.name: ex2TransportSmtpSendTable
ex2TransportSmtpSendTable.description: A table containing performance information for instances of 'MSExchangeTransport SmtpSend' objects.

ex2TransportSmtpSendEntry.name: ex2TransportSmtpSendEntry
ex2TransportSmtpSendEntry.description: Performance information for one particular instance of 'MSExchangeTransport SmtpSend' object.

ex2tssAverageBytesPerConnection.name: ex2tssAverageBytesPerConnection
ex2tssAverageBytesPerConnection.description: Average Bytes/Connection is the average number of bytes per connection sent by this SMTP Send connector.

ex2tssAvgMessageBytesPerMessage.name: ex2tssAvgMessageBytesPerMessage
ex2tssAvgMessageBytesPerMessage.description: Average Message Bytes/Message is the average number of bytes per message sent by this SMTP Send connector.

ex2tssAvgMessagesPerConnection.name: ex2tssAvgMessagesPerConnection
ex2tssAvgMessagesPerConnection.description: Average Messages/Connection is the average number of messages per connection sent by this SMTP Send connector.

ex2tssAvgRecipientsPerMessage.name: ex2tssAvgRecipientsPerMessage
ex2tssAvgRecipientsPerMessage.description: Average Recipients/Message is the average recipients per message handled by this SMTP Send connector.

ex2tssBytesSentTotal.name: ex2tssBytesSentTotal
ex2tssBytesSentTotal.description: Bytes Sent Total is the total number of bytes sent.

ex2tssBytesSentPerSec.name: ex2tssBytesSentPerSec
ex2tssBytesSentPerSec.description: Bytes Sent/sec is the number of bytes sent per second.

ex2tssConnectionsCreatedPerSec.name: ex2tssConnectionsCreatedPerSec
ex2tssConnectionsCreatedPerSec.description: Connections Created/sec is the number of outbound connections established each second from the SMTP Send connector.

ex2tssConnectionsCurrent.name: ex2tssConnectionsCurrent
ex2tssConnectionsCurrent.description: Connections Current is the number of outbound connections from the SMTP Send connector.

ex2tssConnectionsTotal.name: ex2tssConnectionsTotal
ex2tssConnectionsTotal.description: Connections Total is the number of connections ever made from the SMTP Send connector.

ex2tssMessageBytesSentTotal.name: ex2tssMessageBytesSentTotal
ex2tssMessageBytesSentTotal.description: Message Bytes Sent Total is the total number of bytes sent. This number includes only those messages that were successfully sent.

ex2tssMessageBytesSentPerSec.name: ex2tssMessageBytesSentPerSec
ex2tssMessageBytesSentPerSec.description: Message Bytes Sent/sec is the number of bytes sent per second.

ex2tssMessagesSentTotal.name: ex2tssMessagesSentTotal
ex2tssMessagesSentTotal.description: Messages Sent Total is the number of messages sent by the SMTP Send connector.

ex2tssMessagesSentPerSec.name: ex2tssMessagesSentPerSec
ex2tssMessagesSentPerSec.description: Messages Sent/sec is the number of messages sent by the SMTP Send connector each second.

ex2tssRecipientsSent.name: ex2tssRecipientsSent
ex2tssRecipientsSent.description: Recipients sent is the number of recipients sent by the SMTPSend Connector.

ex2UMAutoAttendantTable.name: ex2UMAutoAttendantTable
ex2UMAutoAttendantTable.description: A table containing performance information for instances of 'MSExchangeUMAutoAttendant' objects.

ex2UMAutoAttendantEntry.name: ex2UMAutoAttendantEntry
ex2UMAutoAttendantEntry.description: Performance information for one particular instance of 'MSExchangeUMAutoAttendant' object.

ex2umaaPercentSuccessfulCalls.name: ex2umaaPercentSuccessfulCalls
ex2umaaPercentSuccessfulCalls.description: This counter calculates the success rate of the auto attendant.

ex2umaaAmbiguousNameTransfers.name: ex2umaaAmbiguousNameTransfers
ex2umaaAmbiguousNameTransfers.description: Ambiguous Name Transfers is the number of times that a caller was transferred to the operator because the name that they spelled or spoke was too common in the search results.

ex2umaaAverageCallTime.name: ex2umaaAverageCallTime
ex2umaaAverageCallTime.description: Average Call Time is the average length of time that callers interacted with the auto attendant.

ex2umaaAverageRecentCallTime.name: ex2umaaAverageRecentCallTime
ex2umaaAverageRecentCallTime.description: Average Recent Call Time is the average length of time, in seconds, of the last 50 auto attendant calls.

ex2umaaBusinessHoursCalls.name: ex2umaaBusinessHoursCalls
ex2umaaBusinessHoursCalls.description: Business Hours Calls is the number of calls processed by this auto attendant during business hours.

ex2umaaCallsDisconUMIrreExtError.name: ex2umaaCallsDisconUMIrreExtError
ex2umaaCallsDisconUMIrreExtError.description: Calls Disconnected by UM on Irrecoverable External Error is the total number of calls that were disconnected after an irrecoverable external error occurred.

ex2umaaCallsWithDTMFFallback.name: ex2umaaCallsWithDTMFFallback
ex2umaaCallsWithDTMFFallback.description: Calls with DTMF fallback is the number of calls to this auto attendant during which a caller has been passed to the DTMF fallback auto attendant. This only happens for speech-enabled auto attendants.

ex2umaaCallsWithSentMessage.name: ex2umaaCallsWithSentMessage
ex2umaaCallsWithSentMessage.description: Calls with Sent Message is the number of calls to this auto attendant in which a caller has sent a voice message.

ex2umaaCallsWithSpeechInput.name: ex2umaaCallsWithSpeechInput
ex2umaaCallsWithSpeechInput.description: Calls with Speech Input is the total number of calls during which the caller is determined to have spoken at least once.

ex2umaaCallsWithSpokenName.name: ex2umaaCallsWithSpokenName
ex2umaaCallsWithSpokenName.description: Calls with Spoken Name is the number of calls to this auto attendant in which a caller has spoken a name at least once.

ex2umaaCustomMenuOptions.name: ex2umaaCustomMenuOptions
ex2umaaCustomMenuOptions.description: Custom Menu Options is the number of times that callers have selected custom menu options.

ex2umaaDirectoryAccessed.name: ex2umaaDirectoryAccessed
ex2umaaDirectoryAccessed.description: Directory Accessed is the number of directory access operations performed by this auto attendant.

ex2umaaDirAccsdSuccByDialByName.name: ex2umaaDirAccsdSuccByDialByName
ex2umaaDirAccsdSuccByDialByName.description: Directory Accessed Successfully by Dial by Name is the number of successful directory access operations in which the caller used the Dial by Name feature.

ex2umaaDirAccsdSuccBySpokenName.name: ex2umaaDirAccsdSuccBySpokenName
ex2umaaDirAccsdSuccBySpokenName.description: Directory Accessed Successfully by Spoken Name is the number of successful directory access operations in which the caller used the Dial by Name feature.

ex2umaaDirAccsdByDialByName.name: ex2umaaDirAccsdByDialByName
ex2umaaDirAccsdByDialByName.description: Directory Accessed by Dial by Name is the number of directory access operations in which the subscriber used the Dial by Name feature.

ex2umaaDirAccsdByExtension.name: ex2umaaDirAccsdByExtension
ex2umaaDirAccsdByExtension.description: Directory Accessed by Extension is the number of directory access operations in which the user supplied the extension number.

ex2umaaDirAccsdBySpokenName.name: ex2umaaDirAccsdBySpokenName
ex2umaaDirAccsdBySpokenName.description: Directory Accessed by Spoken Name is the number of directory access operations in which the subscriber spoke a recipient name.

ex2umaaDisallowedTransfers.name: ex2umaaDisallowedTransfers
ex2umaaDisallowedTransfers.description: Disallowed Transfers is the number of times a caller was transferred to the operator because the user they identified was configured to accept calls only from users who are logged on.

ex2umaaDisconnectedWithoutInput.name: ex2umaaDisconnectedWithoutInput
ex2umaaDisconnectedWithoutInput.description: Disconnected Without Input is the number of calls that were dropped without any input being offered in response to the auto attendant prompts.

ex2umaaMenuOption1Used.name: ex2umaaMenuOption1Used
ex2umaaMenuOption1Used.description: Menu Option 1 Used is the number of times that a caller has chosen option 1 from the custom menu.

ex2umaaMenuOption2Used.name: ex2umaaMenuOption2Used
ex2umaaMenuOption2Used.description: Menu Option 2 Used is the number of times that a caller has chosen option 2 from the custom menu.

ex2umaaMenuOption3Used.name: ex2umaaMenuOption3Used
ex2umaaMenuOption3Used.description: Menu Option 3 Used is the number of times that a caller has chosen option 3 from the custom menu.

ex2umaaMenuOption4Used.name: ex2umaaMenuOption4Used
ex2umaaMenuOption4Used.description: Menu Option 4 Used is the number of times that a caller has chosen option 4 from the custom menu.

ex2umaaMenuOption5Used.name: ex2umaaMenuOption5Used
ex2umaaMenuOption5Used.description: Menu Option 5 Used is the number of times that a caller has chosen option 5 from the custom menu.

ex2umaaMenuOption6Used.name: ex2umaaMenuOption6Used
ex2umaaMenuOption6Used.description: Menu Option 6 Used is the number of times that a caller has chosen option 6 from the custom menu.

ex2umaaMenuOption7Used.name: ex2umaaMenuOption7Used
ex2umaaMenuOption7Used.description: Menu Option 7 Used is the number of times that a caller has chosen option 7 from the custom menu.

ex2umaaMenuOption8Used.name: ex2umaaMenuOption8Used
ex2umaaMenuOption8Used.description: Menu Option 8 Used is the number of times that a caller has chosen option 8 from the custom menu.

ex2umaaMenuOption9Used.name: ex2umaaMenuOption9Used
ex2umaaMenuOption9Used.description: Menu Option 9 Used is the number of times that a caller has chosen option 9 from the custom menu.

ex2umaaMenuOptionTimedOut.name: ex2umaaMenuOptionTimedOut
ex2umaaMenuOptionTimedOut.description: Menu Option Timed Out is the number of times that the system has timed out while waiting for a caller to select an option from the custom menu.

ex2umaaOperatorTransfers.name: ex2umaaOperatorTransfers
ex2umaaOperatorTransfers.description: Operator Transfers is the number of calls that have been transferred to the operator.

ex2umaaOperTransReqByUser.name: ex2umaaOperTransReqByUser
ex2umaaOperTransReqByUser.description: Operator Transfers Requested by User is the number of times that a caller to this auto attendant has asked to be transferred to an operator.

ex2umaaOperTransReqByUseOpenMenu.name: ex2umaaOperTransReqByUseOpenMenu
ex2umaaOperTransReqByUseOpenMenu.description: Operator Transfers Requested by User from Opening Menu is the number of times that a caller to this auto attendant has asked to be transferred to an operator while at the opening menu.

ex2umaaOutOfHoursCalls.name: ex2umaaOutOfHoursCalls
ex2umaaOutOfHoursCalls.description: Out of Hours Calls is the number of calls that have been processed by this auto attendant outside of business hours.

ex2umaaSentToAutoAttendant.name: ex2umaaSentToAutoAttendant
ex2umaaSentToAutoAttendant.description: Sent to Auto Attendant is the number of times that a caller to this auto attendant has used the custom menu to go to an auto attendant.

ex2umaaTotalCalls.name: ex2umaaTotalCalls
ex2umaaTotalCalls.description: Total Calls is the number of calls that have been processed by this auto attendant.

ex2umaaTransferredCount.name: ex2umaaTransferredCount
ex2umaaTransferredCount.description: Transferred Count is the number of calls that were transferred by this auto attendant. This number does not include calls that were transferred by the operator.

ex2umaCallAnswerQueuedMessages.name: ex2umaCallAnswerQueuedMessages
ex2umaCallAnswerQueuedMessages.description: Call Answer Queued Messages is the number of messages created and not yet submitted for delivery.

ex2umaCalDisconUMIrrecovExtError.name: ex2umaCalDisconUMIrrecovExtError
ex2umaCalDisconUMIrrecovExtError.description: Calls Disconnected by UM on Irrecoverable External Error is the total number of calls disconnected after an irrecoverable external error occurred.

ex2umaCalDiscnUMIrrecovExtErrSec.name: ex2umaCalDiscnUMIrrecovExtErrSec
ex2umaCalDiscnUMIrrecovExtErrSec.description: Calls Disconnected by UM on Irrecoverable External Error per second is the number of calls disconnected after an irrecoverable external error occurred in the last second.

ex2umaCalDiscnIrrecovInternalErr.name: ex2umaCalDiscnIrrecovInternalErr
ex2umaCalDiscnIrrecovInternalErr.description: Calls Disconnected on Irrecoverable Internal Error is the number of calls disconnected after an internal system error occurred.

ex2umaDirectoryAccessFailures.name: ex2umaDirectoryAccessFailures
ex2umaDirectoryAccessFailures.description: Directory Access Failures is the number of times that attempts to access Active Directory failed.

ex2umaFailedToRedirectCall.name: ex2umaFailedToRedirectCall
ex2umaFailedToRedirectCall.description: Failed to Redirect Call is the number of times the Microsoft Exchange Unified Messaging service did not redirect calls to a UM worker process.

ex2umaHubTransportAccessComplete.name: ex2umaHubTransportAccessComplete
ex2umaHubTransportAccessComplete.description: Hub Transport Access Completed is the number of times that the Hub Transport server was accessed successfully.

ex2umaHubTransportAccessFailures.name: ex2umaHubTransportAccessFailures
ex2umaHubTransportAccessFailures.description: Hub Transport Access Failures is the number of times that attempts to access a Hub Transport server failed. This number is only incremented if all Hub Transport servers were unavailable.

ex2umaIncompSignalingInformation.name: ex2umaIncompSignalingInformation
ex2umaIncompSignalingInformation.description: Incomplete Signaling Information is the number of calls for which the signaling information was missing or incomplete.

ex2umaMailboxServerAccessFailure.name: ex2umaMailboxServerAccessFailure
ex2umaMailboxServerAccessFailure.description: Mailbox Server Access Failures is the number of times the system did not access a Mailbox server.

ex2umaMaximumCallsAllowed.name: ex2umaMaximumCallsAllowed
ex2umaMaximumCallsAllowed.description: Maximum Calls Allowed is the length of time, in seconds, that the server concurrently processed the maximum number of calls allowed.

ex2umaNameTTSed.name: ex2umaNameTTSed
ex2umaNameTTSed.description: Name TTSed is the number of times the system used Text-to-Speech (TTS) to create an audio version of the display name of a subscriber.

ex2umaQueuedOCSUserEventNotifica.name: ex2umaQueuedOCSUserEventNotifica
ex2umaQueuedOCSUserEventNotifica.description: Queued OCS User Event Notifications is the number of notifications that have been created and not yet submitted for delivery.

ex2umaSpokenNameAccessed.name: ex2umaSpokenNameAccessed
ex2umaSpokenNameAccessed.description: Spoken Name Accessed is the number of times the system retrieved the recorded name of a user.

ex2umaTotalWorkerProcesCallCount.name: ex2umaTotalWorkerProcesCallCount
ex2umaTotalWorkerProcesCallCount.description: Total Worker Process Call Count is the total number of calls handled by this UM worker process.

ex2umaUnhandledExceptionsPerSec.name: ex2umaUnhandledExceptionsPerSec
ex2umaUnhandledExceptionsPerSec.description: Calls Disconnected on Irrecoverable Internal Error Per Second is the number of calls that were disconnected after an internal system error occurred in the last second.

ex2umaWorkerProcessRecycled.name: ex2umaWorkerProcessRecycled
ex2umaWorkerProcessRecycled.description: Worker Process Recycled is the number of times a new UM worker process has been started.

ex2UMCallAnsAvgGreetingSize.name: ex2UMCallAnsAvgGreetingSize
ex2UMCallAnsAvgGreetingSize.description: Average Greeting Size is the average size, in seconds, of recorded greetings that have been retrieved by the UM server.

ex2UMCallAnsAvgRecentVoiceMsgSiz.name: ex2UMCallAnsAvgRecentVoiceMsgSiz
ex2UMCallAnsAvgRecentVoiceMsgSiz.description: Average Recent Voice Message Size is the average size, in seconds, of the last 50 voice messages that have been left for subscribers.

ex2UMCallAnsAvgVoiceMsgSize.name: ex2UMCallAnsAvgVoiceMsgSize
ex2UMCallAnsAvgVoiceMsgSize.description: Average Voice Message Size is the average size, in seconds, of voice messages left for subscribers.

ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsingCalls.name: ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsingCalls
ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsingCalls.description: Call Answering Calls is the number of diverted calls that were answered on behalf of subscribers.

ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsingEscapes.name: ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsingEscapes
ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsingEscapes.description: Call Answering Escapes is the number of times a caller pressed the * key to connect to another user rather than leaving a message.

ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsingMissedCall.name: ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsingMissedCall
ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsingMissedCall.description: Call Answering Missed Calls is the number of times a diverted call was dropped without a message being left.

ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsingVoiceMsgs.name: ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsingVoiceMsgs
ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsingVoiceMsgs.description: Call Answering Voice Messages is the total number of messages that were submitted because the calls were answered on behalf of subscribers.

ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsVoiceMsgPrSec.name: ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsVoiceMsgPrSec
ex2UMCallAnsCallAnsVoiceMsgPrSec.description: Call Answering Voice Messages per Second is the number of messages that were submitted because the calls were answered on behalf of subscribers.

ex2UMCallAnsCallFailTransUnavail.name: ex2UMCallAnsCallFailTransUnavail
ex2UMCallAnsCallFailTransUnavail.description: Call Failed Because Transport Unavailable is the number of calls that failed because the transport service is not available to submit the message.

ex2UMCalAnsCalDisCalUMAudioHrgls.name: ex2UMCalAnsCalDisCalUMAudioHrgls
ex2UMCalAnsCalDisCalUMAudioHrgls.description: Calls Disconnected by Callers During UM Audio Hourglass is the number of calls during which the caller disconnected while Unified Messaging was playing the audio hourglass tones.

ex2UMCalAnsCalDisUMIrrecExtError.name: ex2UMCalAnsCalDisUMIrrecExtError
ex2UMCalAnsCalDisUMIrrecExtError.description: Calls Disconnected by UM on Irrecoverable External Error is the total number of calls that have been disconnected after an irrecoverable external error occurred.

ex2UMCallAnsCallWithoutPersGreet.name: ex2UMCallAnsCallWithoutPersGreet
ex2UMCallAnsCallWithoutPersGreet.description: Calls Without Personal Greetings is the number of diverted calls received for subscribers that did not have recorded greeting messages.

ex2UMCallAnsDivertExtNotProvis.name: ex2UMCallAnsDivertExtNotProvis
ex2UMCallAnsDivertExtNotProvis.description: Diverted Extension Not Provisioned is the number of calls received for which the diverted extension supplied with the call is not a UM subscriber extension.

ex2UMCallAnsFetchGreetingTimeOut.name: ex2UMCallAnsFetchGreetingTimeOut
ex2UMCallAnsFetchGreetingTimeOut.description: Fetch Greeting Timed Out is the number of diverted calls for which the subscriber's personal greeting could not be retrieved within the time allowed.

ex2UMClientAccessTable.name: ex2UMClientAccessTable
ex2UMClientAccessTable.description: A table containing performance information for instances of 'MSExchangeUMClientAccess' objects.

ex2UMClientAccessEntry.name: ex2UMClientAccessEntry
ex2UMClientAccessEntry.description: Performance information for one particular instance of 'MSExchangeUMClientAccess' object.

ex2umcacPID.name: ex2umcacPID
ex2umcacPID.description: Process ID that is hosting the UM client access component

ex2umcacTotalNumPINResetRequests.name: ex2umcacTotalNumPINResetRequests
ex2umcacTotalNumPINResetRequests.description: Total Number of PIN Reset Requests is the number of PIN resets that have been requested since the host process was restarted.

ex2umcacTotalNumFailPINResetReq.name: ex2umcacTotalNumFailPINResetReq
ex2umcacTotalNumFailPINResetReq.description: Total Number of Failed PIN Reset Requests is the number of requested PIN resets that have failed since the host process was restarted.

ex2umcacTotalNumFailPlayPhoneReq.name: ex2umcacTotalNumFailPlayPhoneReq
ex2umcacTotalNumFailPlayPhoneReq.description: Total number of failed play on phone requests since the host process was restarted

ex2umcacTotalNumPlayPhoneRequest.name: ex2umcacTotalNumPlayPhoneRequest
ex2umcacTotalNumPlayPhoneRequest.description: Total number of play on phone requests since the host process was restarted

ex2umfAverageFaxMessageSize.name: ex2umfAverageFaxMessageSize
ex2umfAverageFaxMessageSize.description: Average Fax Message Size is the average size, in kilobytes, of fax messages received.

ex2umfAverageRecentFaxMessageSiz.name: ex2umfAverageRecentFaxMessageSiz
ex2umfAverageRecentFaxMessageSiz.description: Average Recent Fax Message Size is the average size, in kilobytes, of the last 20 fax messages.

ex2umfFaxCallDurationExceeded.name: ex2umfFaxCallDurationExceeded
ex2umfFaxCallDurationExceeded.description: Fax Call Duration Exceeded is the number of fax calls that were disconnected because they exceeded the UM maximum call length.

ex2umfFaxCallNonProvisionMailbox.name: ex2umfFaxCallNonProvisionMailbox
ex2umfFaxCallNonProvisionMailbox.description: Fax Calls to Non Provisioned Mailboxes is the number of calls to extensions that resolved to mailboxes that are not enabled for fax.

ex2umfFaxIncomplete.name: ex2umfFaxIncomplete
ex2umfFaxIncomplete.description: Fax Incomplete is the number of fax calls that were dropped before completion.

ex2umfFaxMessages.name: ex2umfFaxMessages
ex2umfFaxMessages.description: Fax Messages is the total number of fax messages received.

ex2umgAverageCallDuration.name: ex2umgAverageCallDuration
ex2umgAverageCallDuration.description: Average Call Duration is the average duration, in seconds, of calls since the service was started.

ex2umgAverageRecentCallDuration.name: ex2umgAverageRecentCallDuration
ex2umgAverageRecentCallDuration.description: Average Recent Call Duration is the average duration, in seconds, of the last 50 calls.

ex2umgCallDurationExceeded.name: ex2umgCallDurationExceeded
ex2umgCallDurationExceeded.description: Call Duration Exceeded is the number of calls that were disconnected because they exceeded the UM maximum call length. This number includes all types of calls, including fax calls.

ex2umgCallsDisconnectUserFailure.name: ex2umgCallsDisconnectUserFailure
ex2umgCallsDisconnectUserFailure.description: Calls Disconnected by User Failure is the total number of calls disconnected after too many user entry failures.

ex2umgCallsRejected.name: ex2umgCallsRejected
ex2umgCallsRejected.description: Calls Rejected is the total number of new call invitations that have been rejected.

ex2umgCallsRejectedPerSecond.name: ex2umgCallsRejectedPerSecond
ex2umgCallsRejectedPerSecond.description: Calls Rejected per Second is the number of new call invitations that have been rejected in the last second.

ex2umgCurrentAutoAttendantCalls.name: ex2umgCurrentAutoAttendantCalls
ex2umgCurrentAutoAttendantCalls.description: Current Auto Attendant Calls is the number of auto attendant calls that are currently connected to the UM server.

ex2umgCurrentCASConnections.name: ex2umgCurrentCASConnections
ex2umgCurrentCASConnections.description: Current CAS Connections is the number of connections that are currently open between the Unified Messaging server and Client Access servers.

ex2umgCurrentCalls.name: ex2umgCurrentCalls
ex2umgCurrentCalls.description: Current Calls is the number of calls that are currently connected to the UM server.

ex2umgCurrentFaxCalls.name: ex2umgCurrentFaxCalls
ex2umgCurrentFaxCalls.description: Current Fax Calls is the number of fax calls that are currently connected to the UM server. Voice calls become fax calls after a fax tone is detected.

ex2umgCurrentPlayOnPhoneCalls.name: ex2umgCurrentPlayOnPhoneCalls
ex2umgCurrentPlayOnPhoneCalls.description: Current Play on Phone Calls is the number of outbound calls that were initiated to play back messages.

ex2umgCurrentPromptEditingCalls.name: ex2umgCurrentPromptEditingCalls
ex2umgCurrentPromptEditingCalls.description: Current Prompt Editing Calls is the number of logged on users who are editing custom prompts.

ex2umgCurrentSubscriberAccesCall.name: ex2umgCurrentSubscriberAccesCall
ex2umgCurrentSubscriberAccesCall.description: Current Subscriber Access Calls is the number of logged on subscribers who are currently connected to the UM server.

ex2umgCurrUnauthentPilotNumCall.name: ex2umgCurrUnauthentPilotNumCall
ex2umgCurrUnauthentPilotNumCall.description: Current Unauthenticated Pilot Number Calls is the number of voice calls to the pilot number that have not yet been authenticated.

ex2umgCurrentVoiceCalls.name: ex2umgCurrentVoiceCalls
ex2umgCurrentVoiceCalls.description: Current Voice Calls is the number of voice calls that are currently connected to the UM server.

ex2umgDelayedCalls.name: ex2umgDelayedCalls
ex2umgDelayedCalls.description: Delayed Calls is the number of calls that experienced one or more delays longer than 2 seconds.

ex2umgOCSUserEventNotifications.name: ex2umgOCSUserEventNotifications
ex2umgOCSUserEventNotifications.description: OCS User Event Notifications is the total number of OCS User Event notifications that have occurred since the service was started.

ex2umgTotalCalls.name: ex2umgTotalCalls
ex2umgTotalCalls.description: Total Calls is the number of calls since the service was started.

ex2umgTotalCallsPerSecond.name: ex2umgTotalCallsPerSecond
ex2umgTotalCallsPerSecond.description: Total Calls per Second is the number of new calls that have arrived in the last second.

ex2umgTotalPlayOnPhoneCalls.name: ex2umgTotalPlayOnPhoneCalls
ex2umgTotalPlayOnPhoneCalls.description: Total Play on Phone Calls is the total number of Play on Phone calls that have been initiated since the service was started.

ex2umgUserResponseLatency.name: ex2umgUserResponseLatency
ex2umgUserResponseLatency.description: User Response Latency is the average response time, in milliseconds, for the system to respond to a user request. This average is calculated over the last 25 calls. This counter is limited to calls that require significant processing.

ex2umpOperationsOverFiveSeconds.name: ex2umpOperationsOverFiveSeconds
ex2umpOperationsOverFiveSeconds.description: Operations over Five Seconds is the number of all UM operations that took between 5 and 6 seconds to complete. This is the time during which a caller was waiting for UM to respond.

ex2umpOperationsOverFourSeconds.name: ex2umpOperationsOverFourSeconds
ex2umpOperationsOverFourSeconds.description: Operations over Four Seconds is the number of all UM operations that took between 4 and 5 seconds to complete. This is the time during which a caller was waiting for UM to respond.

ex2umpOperationsOverSixSeconds.name: ex2umpOperationsOverSixSeconds
ex2umpOperationsOverSixSeconds.description: Operations over Six Seconds is the number of all UM operations that took more than 6 seconds to complete. This is the time during which a caller was waiting for UM to respond.

ex2umpOperationsOverThreeSeconds.name: ex2umpOperationsOverThreeSeconds
ex2umpOperationsOverThreeSeconds.description: Operations over Three Seconds is the number of all UM operations that took between 3 and 4 seconds to complete. This is the time during which a caller was waiting for UM to respond.

ex2umpOperationsOverTwoSeconds.name: ex2umpOperationsOverTwoSeconds
ex2umpOperationsOverTwoSeconds.description: Operations over Two Seconds is the number of all UM operations that took between 2 and 3 seconds to complete. This is the time during which a caller was waiting for UM to respond.

ex2umpOperationsUnderTwoSeconds.name: ex2umpOperationsUnderTwoSeconds
ex2umpOperationsUnderTwoSeconds.description: Operations under Two Seconds is the number of all UM operations that took less than 2 seconds to complete. This is the time during which a caller was waiting for UM to respond.

ex2umsaAvgRecentSentVoiceMsgSize.name: ex2umsaAvgRecentSentVoiceMsgSize
ex2umsaAvgRecentSentVoiceMsgSize.description: Average Recent Sent Voice Message Size is the average size, in seconds, of the last 50 voice messages that were sent.

ex2umsaAvgRecentSubscribeCallDur.name: ex2umsaAvgRecentSubscribeCallDur
ex2umsaAvgRecentSubscribeCallDur.description: Average Subscriber Recent Call Duration is the average length of time, in seconds, that subscribers spent logged on to the system for the last 50 subscriber calls.

ex2umsaAvgSentVoiceMessageSize.name: ex2umsaAvgSentVoiceMessageSize
ex2umsaAvgSentVoiceMessageSize.description: Average Sent Voice Message Size is the average size, in seconds, of voice messages that are sent. This size does not include any attachment data.

ex2umsaAvgSubscriberCallDuration.name: ex2umsaAvgSubscriberCallDuration
ex2umsaAvgSubscriberCallDuration.description: Average Subscriber Call Duration is the average duration, in seconds, that subscribers spent logged on to the system. This timer starts when logon completes.

ex2umsaCalendarAccessed.name: ex2umsaCalendarAccessed
ex2umsaCalendarAccessed.description: Calendar Accessed is the number of times subscribers accessed their calendars using the telephone user interface.

ex2umsaCalendarItemDetailRequest.name: ex2umsaCalendarItemDetailRequest
ex2umsaCalendarItemDetailRequest.description: Calendar Items Details Requested is the number of times a subscriber requested additional details for a calendar item.

ex2umsaCalendarItemsHeard.name: ex2umsaCalendarItemsHeard
ex2umsaCalendarItemsHeard.description: Calendar Items Heard is the number of Calendar items that have been heard by authenticated subscribers.

ex2umsaCalendarLateAttendance.name: ex2umsaCalendarLateAttendance
ex2umsaCalendarLateAttendance.description: Calendar Late Attendance is the number of messages that have been sent to inform the organizer of a meeting that the subscriber will be late.

ex2umsaCalledMeetingOrganizer.name: ex2umsaCalledMeetingOrganizer
ex2umsaCalledMeetingOrganizer.description: Called Meeting Organizer is the number of times subscribers called the meeting organizer.

ex2umsaCalDiscCalDurUMAudioHrgls.name: ex2umsaCalDiscCalDurUMAudioHrgls
ex2umsaCalDiscCalDurUMAudioHrgls.description: Calls Disconnected by Callers During UM Audio Hourglass is the number of calls in which the caller disconnected while UM was playing the audio hourglass tones.

ex2umsaCallDisUMOnIrrecvExtError.name: ex2umsaCallDisUMOnIrrecvExtError
ex2umsaCallDisUMOnIrrecvExtError.description: Calls Disconnected by UM on Irrecoverable External Error is the total number of calls that have been disconnected after an irrecoverable external error occurred.

ex2umsaContactItemsHeard.name: ex2umsaContactItemsHeard
ex2umsaContactItemsHeard.description: Contact Items Heard is the number of times authenticated subscribers listened to directory details.

ex2umsaContactsAccessed.name: ex2umsaContactsAccessed
ex2umsaContactsAccessed.description: Contacts Accessed is the number of times subscribers accessed the Main Menu Contacts option using the telephone user interface.

ex2umsaDirectoryAccessed.name: ex2umsaDirectoryAccessed
ex2umsaDirectoryAccessed.description: Directory Accessed is the number of times subscribers accessed the Main Menu Directory option by using the telephone user interface.

ex2umsaDirAccsdSuccessDialName.name: ex2umsaDirAccsdSuccessDialName
ex2umsaDirAccsdSuccessDialName.description: Directory Accessed Successfully by Dial by Name is the number of Dial by Name directory access operations that completed successfully on behalf of subscribers.

ex2umsaDirAccsdSuccessSpokenName.name: ex2umsaDirAccsdSuccessSpokenName
ex2umsaDirAccsdSuccessSpokenName.description: Directory Accessed Successfully by Spoken Name is the number of speech recognition directory access operations that completed successfully on behalf of subscribers.

ex2umsaDirAccsdByDialByName.name: ex2umsaDirAccsdByDialByName
ex2umsaDirAccsdByDialByName.description: Directory Accessed by Dial by Name is the number of directory access operations where the subscriber used the Dial by Name feature.

ex2umsaDirAccsdByExtension.name: ex2umsaDirAccsdByExtension
ex2umsaDirAccsdByExtension.description: Directory Accessed by Extension is the number of directory access operations in which the user supplied the extension number.

ex2umsaDirAccsdBySpokenName.name: ex2umsaDirAccsdBySpokenName
ex2umsaDirAccsdBySpokenName.description: Directory Accessed by Spoken Name is the number of directory access operations in which the subscriber spoke a recipient name.

ex2umsaEmailMessageQueueAccessed.name: ex2umsaEmailMessageQueueAccessed
ex2umsaEmailMessageQueueAccessed.description: Email Message Queue Accessed is the number of times subscribers accessed their e-mail message queue by using the telephone user interface.

ex2umsaEmailMessagesDeleted.name: ex2umsaEmailMessagesDeleted
ex2umsaEmailMessagesDeleted.description: Email Messages Deleted is the number of e-mail messages that were deleted by authenticated subscribers.

ex2umsaEmailMessagesHeard.name: ex2umsaEmailMessagesHeard
ex2umsaEmailMessagesHeard.description: Email Messages Heard is the number of e-mail messages that have been heard by authenticated subscribers.

ex2umsaForwardMessagesSent.name: ex2umsaForwardMessagesSent
ex2umsaForwardMessagesSent.description: Forward Messages Sent is the number of messages that have been forwarded by authenticated subscribers.

ex2umsaLaunchedCalls.name: ex2umsaLaunchedCalls
ex2umsaLaunchedCalls.description: Launched Calls is the number of subscriber calls that resulted in an outbound call being placed.

ex2umsaMeetingsAccepted.name: ex2umsaMeetingsAccepted
ex2umsaMeetingsAccepted.description: Meetings Accepted is the number of Meeting Accepted messages send by subscribers.

ex2umsaMeetingsDeclined.name: ex2umsaMeetingsDeclined
ex2umsaMeetingsDeclined.description: Meetings Declined is the number of Meeting Declined messages sent by subscribers.

ex2umsaRepliedToOrganizer.name: ex2umsaRepliedToOrganizer
ex2umsaRepliedToOrganizer.description: Replied to Organizer is the number of times subscribers sent reply messages to meeting organizers.

ex2umsaReplyMessagesSent.name: ex2umsaReplyMessagesSent
ex2umsaReplyMessagesSent.description: Reply Messages Sent is the number of replies sent by authenticated subscribers.

ex2umsaSubscriberAuthentFailure.name: ex2umsaSubscriberAuthentFailure
ex2umsaSubscriberAuthentFailure.description: Subscriber Authentication Failures is the number of authentication failures that have occurred since the service was started. This number is incremented once for every failed authentication. It is possible that a single phone call could generate several authentication failures.

ex2umsaSubscriberLogonFailures.name: ex2umsaSubscriberLogonFailures
ex2umsaSubscriberLogonFailures.description: Subscriber Logon Failures is the number of logon failures since the service was started. This number is incremented at most once per phone call.

ex2umsaSubscriberLogons.name: ex2umsaSubscriberLogons
ex2umsaSubscriberLogons.description: Subscriber Logons is the number of successful authentications by UM subscribers since the service was started.

ex2umsaVoiceMessageQueueAccessed.name: ex2umsaVoiceMessageQueueAccessed
ex2umsaVoiceMessageQueueAccessed.description: Voice Message Queue Accessed is the number of times subscribers accessed their voice message queues by using the telephone user interface.

ex2umsaVoiceMessagesDeleted.name: ex2umsaVoiceMessagesDeleted
ex2umsaVoiceMessagesDeleted.description: Voice Messages Deleted is the number of voice messages that were deleted by authenticated subscribers.

ex2umsaVoiceMessagesHeard.name: ex2umsaVoiceMessagesHeard
ex2umsaVoiceMessagesHeard.description: Voice Messages Heard is the number of voice messages played to subscribers. This count is incremented as soon as playback starts. The subscriber does not need to listen to the entire message.

ex2umsaVoiceMessagesSent.name: ex2umsaVoiceMessagesSent
ex2umsaVoiceMessagesSent.description: Voice Messages Sent is the number of voice messages that have been sent by authenticated UM subscribers.

ex2WSActiveSubscriptions.name: ex2WSActiveSubscriptions
ex2WSActiveSubscriptions.description: Active Subscriptions is the number of active subscriptions.
